    "Details": "The original New Dawn is built for mid-to-long range combat, pairing a Rotary AC/5 for sustained ballistic output with a Heavy PPC that delivers a devastating single punch at the cost of enormous heat. Three ER Medium Lasers fill out the ranged arsenal. Four jump jets give the 75-ton frame meaningful positional flexibility. Sixteen double heat sinks keep the loadout manageable when pilots avoid firing everything simultaneously.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>",
